excerpt.rendered:
OCCASION ALERT

This well maintained Bullit 600 inboard has sailed in and around the waters of Belt Schutsloot. The aluminum tender is 6 meters long and 2.15 meters wide. The draft is 40 centimeters and the vertical clearance is 1.12 meters.

The boat is equipped with
  1. LED navigation lights red/green. 360 degrees removable white light and 12 Volt plug;
  2. Complete cushions of Sunbrella;
  3. Sun bed with wooden bottom;
  4. Hydraulic steering;
  5. Waterproof cover for steering console;
  6. Bimini top;
  7. Stainless steel swim ladder;
  8. Stainless steel flagpole holder with NL flag;
  9. STAZO anti-theft lock;
  10. Marine radio;
  11. 2 cone fenders and 4 mooring lines;
  12. 28 HP Vetus inboard engine.

Other data about the Bullit 600 inboard model can be found here

Are you interested in this boat? Do not wait any longer and contact us!
